snippet.title: Amber Heard Shares Her Hopes For #MeToo, 'Aquaman' Character | EXTENDED
snippet.description:
Sangita Patel caught up with L'Oreal ambassador Amber Heard at the Toronto International Film Festival, where the actress shared her hopes for the #MeToo movement and revealed that she signed on to "Aquaman" thanks to her badass "warrior queen" character, Meera.
